      "writtenOn": "2020-03-12T03:56:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "For my own education, how do these version numbers interact with package-lock.json? It looks like these dependencies are all unpinned since they start with ^.\n\nhttps://docs.npmjs.com/misc/semver#caret-ranges-123-025-004",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 9,
        "startChar": 29,
        "endLine": 16,
        "endChar": 23
      },
      "revId": "b097039f958491e89bb43c0c6a523e3194800c15",
